msgctxt " 	　	　	116	1415	1299"
msgid "Dojima came to Fukuoka to butter up\\r\n"
"the local folks personally."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	91	1522	1431"
msgid "And Watase made his way\\r\n"
"down to stop him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	79	1615	1536"
msgid "Stop the alliance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	120	1769	1649"
msgid "Is the Omi trying to beat\\r\n"
"the Tojo Clan to it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1847	1787"
msgid "Beats me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	193	2042	1849"
msgid "All I know is, they're tryin' to keep\\r\n"
"the Tojo from joinin' up with the Yamagasa Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	69	2134	2065"
msgid "And if they don't get what they want..."
