msgctxt " 	　	　	60	4728	4668"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	190	4930	4740"
msgid "If the Watase Family <Italic>did</Italic> kidnap Daigo Dojima,\\r\n"
"sure as shit those two'll jump into action."
