msgctxt " 	　	　	84	5916	5832"
msgid "That's exactly why it has to be you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	98	6033	5935"
msgid "You're the only one who can pull this off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	121	6155	6034"
msgid "Ya got the knowledge, the influence..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	97	6257	6160"
msgid "But you're far enough removed to be impartial."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	120	6393	6273"
msgid "Meanin', you're the perfect guy for the job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	129	6563	6434"
msgid "Imagine it helps that\\r\n"
"you're no slouch in a fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	6653	6593"
msgid "Why can't the police handle it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	157	6820	6663"
msgid "Don't be thick. It wouldn't fix\\r\n"
"a damn thing if we arrested an Omi officer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	96	6930	6834"
msgid "I couldn't even tell you all the\\r\n"
"shit that would set in motion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	130	7081	6951"
msgid "Best thing to do is hold out\\r\n"
"an olive branch, resolve this peacefully."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	70	7204	7134"
msgid "What's in it for you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	118	7350	7232"
msgid "If us Osaka boys get the credit\\r\n"
"instead of the Tokyo blue..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	78	7437	7359"
msgid "Maybe we can finally stop\\r\n"
"grovelin' at their feet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	7556	7496"
msgid "Think you're familiar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	153	7712	7559"
msgid "Lady detective of ours got a little\\r\n"
"<Italic>too</Italic> friendly with this famous yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	119	7844	7725"
msgid "Now our Organized Crime unit's\\r\n"
"the butt of every joke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	201	8075	7874"
msgid "We gotta show 'em that Osaka's still got\\r\n"
"a role to play in these big-time cases."
